data.description: Beautiful log home with mountain views of the Great Smoky Mountains. This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home is situated on a large 1.04-acre tract of land.  This 1 1/2 story log home has a full basement.  Perfect for the kids or mancave.  There is also a very large metal building currently used as a shed craft shop.  This home has a large front porch which is perfect for sipping tea and conversation.  The views are beautiful.  The log home is located just minutes from two of the area's premier lakes!  Douglas and Cherokee. Both lakes are TVA public lakes offering you over 60,000 acres of public water to fish and play upon.  Just 10 miles up the interstate is the Gateway to The Great Smoky Mountain National Park, Dollywood, Splash Country, Bass Pro, Pigeon Forge and Gatlinburg!   The home is just minutes from four of the area schools.  Over 17 million visitors per year come to this area ....but...only the lucky ones get to call this place home.  Be lucky...Book your appointment today!
